Package parser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Arc
    This class defines an object that represents a possible transition in a Finite State Automata (a FSA object).
    FSA
    A Deterministic Finite State Automata (FSA) that defines a regular pattern and tries matching it against an input string.
    FSAStructureBuilder
    Object in charge of building the inner structure of a Finite State Automata (FSA object).
    InputParserBuilder
    This class defines an object intended to change a list of String tags into a correspondent list of textual objects (objects Token).
    Parse
    Script intended to build a FSA and test it
    Parser
    Supertype of all possible parsers (FSA...)
    State
    Defines a state in a Finite State Automata.
    Unificator
    Defines an object able to check if two non-nested feature structures (objects Type) unify.
